observations.recommendation:
We recommended that management to direct the;

Engineering department to submit the necessary documents especially the completion reports of the above mentioned projects to the accounting department.

Accounting department to draw a Journal Entry Voucher (JEV) to  reclassify  the Construction in Progress – Infrastructure Assets account into an  appropriate asset account if the necessary documents are already  at hand. Depreciation applicable for the previous years shall be considered  as  Prior Years’ Adjustments. A copy of the JEV shall be furnished to the office of the Auditor.
